{"type":"message","id":"b9caac9c","parentId":"a3966440","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:22:31.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！从日志可以看出，错误原因是：\n\n```\nFailoverError: Unknown model: qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b\n```\n\nOpenClaw 找不到这个模型标识符。让我查看一下当前配置的模型列表，特别是火山引擎 ARK 自定义模型部分："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ob3t587tgfe2m1tsscto33jt","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/bin/openclaw models list custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","workdir":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":7973,"output":157,"cacheRead":19256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27386,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775546547438,"responseId":"02177554654753678a4d31784aa640fc35612e0bcb929205fe799"}}
