{"type":"message","id":"3548b9ac","parentId":"8f7f834f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:31:31.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了问题！根本原因是 **认证问题**：\n\n```\nNo API key found for provider \"local-gpu\". \nAuth store: /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json\n```\n\n你的 `local-gpu` 提供者在配置文件 `openclaw.json` 中是这样的：\n```json\n\"local-gpu\": {\n  \"baseUrl\": \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\",\n  \"apiKey\": \"\",  // ← 这里是空的！\n  \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n  ...\n}\n```\n\n虽然 apiKey 是空的（本地模型可能不需要认证），但 OpenClaw 的代理认证系统仍然需要在 `auth-profiles.json` 中配置这个提供者的凭证（即使是空的）。\n\n**解决方法：** 按照日志提示，你需要将根配置的认证信息复制到代理目录，或者重新添加代理：\n\n```bash\n# 方案 1：复制认证文件（最简单）\ncp /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/auth-profiles.json /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json\n```\n\n然后重启 Gateway：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n让我先检查一下根目录是否有 `auth-profiles.json`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_sokb6dpxlmql817yi7vw82p4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/ | grep auth","workdir":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":28116,"output":388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28504,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775547082183,"responseId":"02177554708233413d48c4760d2f20ff0aabc46dcd14fa8cb6b83"}}
