{"type":"message","id":"a46f76da","parentId":"e0832a4b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:32:36.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！问题已经解决了。让我总结一下：\n\n## 🔍 问题诊断结果\n\n**根本原因：** `No API key found for provider \"local-gpu\"`\n\nOpenClaw 在根配置目录 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/` 下找不到 `auth-profiles.json` 文件，虽然代理目录 `agents/main/agent/` 下有这个文件，但根目录也需要它。\n\n## ✅ 已完成的修复\n\n1. **创建了缺失的文件**：在 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/` 下创建了 `auth-profiles.json`，包含了 `local-gpu:default` 认证配置（key 为空，符合你的本地模型需求）\n\n2. **Gateway 已重启**，新配置生效\n\n## 📝 验证\n\n从最新日志看，已经没有 `No API key found` 错误了，Gateway 运行正常。现在你可以尝试测试调用 `local-gpu/qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` 模型了。\n\n如果测试成功，你再自己切换默认模型即可。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3902,"output":246,"cacheRead":22328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26476,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775547148701,"responseId":"0217755471487958f8ea30227d9931fee346cda39788dd1f65a49"}}
