{"type":"message","id":"e2ab4be2","parentId":"06b3d572","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:34:44.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在 API key 的问题已经解决了，日志里没有再报 `No API key found` 的错误了。\n\n关于 `session_status` 工具提示 \"Model not allowed\"，这是因为 `session_status` 工具本身有自己的 allowlist 检查，不影响实际对话。\n\n**✅ 当前状态：**\n1. ✅ API key 问题已解决 - `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/auth-profiles.json` 和 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json` 都已正确配置 `local-gpu:default`\n2. ✅ Gateway 已重启，配置生效\n3. ℹ️ `session_status` 的 \"not allowed\" 只是工具本身的限制，不影响实际调用\n\n现在你可以在控制 UI 里发送一条消息测试 `local-gpu/qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` 模型了，应该能正常获得回复。你测试一下看看结果如何？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":4333,"output":218,"cacheRead":24376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28927,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775547278207,"responseId":"021775547278302d72149264581351fe280677b9f79ce08f33edf"}}
