key error for the `local-gpu` provider\n\n### Blocked\n- Agent startup fails because of missing API key configuration for the `local-gpu` provider\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Fix model identifier instead of switching to Volcano Engine**: The user's qwen model is already configured correctly under `local-gpu` provider, only the model ID used was incorrect, so corrected the configuration instead of switching to the Volcano Engine model\n- **Directly modify the openclaw.json configuration file**: Corrected the main agent model setting via direct file edit after failed patching attempts\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Configure an API key for the `local-gpu` provider in the agent auth store at `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json`\n2. Or copy the existing valid auth-profiles.json from the main agent directory to resolve the auth error\n\n## Critical Context\n- User is working with the `openclaw-control-ui` service (metadata label and id: `openclaw-control-ui`)\n- User's custom model: qwen3.5 35b, attempted original model identifier: `qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b`\n- Original error: `FailoverError: Unknown model: qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` - the model identifier was incorrect\n- Correct full model ID: `local-gpu/qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` (model is configured under the `local-gpu` provider, not `qwen` provider)\n- Volcano Engine model is hosted under the provider `custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com`, with only `ark-code-latest` configured\n- OpenClaw configuration file path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- New error after model ID fix: `No API key found for provider \"local-gpu\". Auth store: /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir.`\n- To view logs: run `openclaw logs --follow`\n- To switch back to the original Volcano Engine model, revert the configuration to `custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com/ark-code-latest`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\n用户请求排查自定义模型qwen3.5 35B部署失败的原因，要求先不切换模型，待自行测试成功后再切换。\n\n## Early Progress\n1. 读取日志定位到错误：`local-gpu`提供者找不到API密钥，提示需要配置`auth-profiles.json`\n2. 发现用户openclaw.json中`local-gpu`的apiKey为空，最初判断是代理目录缺少认证配置\n3. 检查确认代理目录`/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/`下已存在`auth-profiles.json`，且其中已经配置了空密钥的`local-gpu:default`认证配置\n4. 确认根目录`/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/`下没有根级`auth-profiles.json`\n5. 下一步准备查看`openclaw.json`中`local-gpu`的完整配置\n\n## Context for Suffix\n已获取`openclaw.json`中`local-gpu`配置的部分结果，需要基于该结果继续分析配置问题。\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"4ddf9b86","tokensBefore":28927,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json"],"modifiedFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json"]},"fromHook":false}
