{"type":"message","id":"9e4cd95d","parentId":"54d33719","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:43:14.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太棒了！我终于找到问题了！\n\n这是本地自定义 provider 的特性：`resolveSyntheticLocalProviderAuth` 会为本地 baseUrl（`127.0.0.1`、`192.168.*`、`10.*`、`172.*` 等内网地址）自动生成一个 synthetic 认证，不需要 API key！\n\n但是你这里的 baseUrl 是 `http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1`，这是一个公网 IP，所以它不被 `isLocalBaseUrl()` 识别，无法触发自动 synthetic 认证。\n\n我们的 `apiKey` 在 provider 配置中已经删除了，但它又不是本地 IP，所以无法生成 synthetic 密钥，也找不到配置好的认证...\n\n等等，`isLocalBaseUrl` 判断逻辑是什么？让我看看：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ywq91vm9bszd4i2wehrof0ff","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n -A 20 \"function isLocalBaseUrl\" /Users/liuchenglong/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/auth-profiles-B5ypC5S-.js","workdir":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":5989,"output":312,"cacheRead":22840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775547789125,"responseId":"021775547789241289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108ae420480"}}
{"type":"message","id":"155cac9b","parentId":"9e4cd95d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:43:14.887Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ywq91vm9bszd4i2wehrof0ff","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"213767:function isLocalBaseUrl(baseUrl) {\n213768-\ttry {\n213769-\t\tconst host = new URL(baseUrl).hostname.toLowerCase();\n213770-\t\treturn host === \"localhost\" || host === \"127.0.0.1\" || host === \"0.0.0.0\" || host === \"[::1]\" || host === \"[::ffff:7f00:1]\" || host === \"[::ffff:127.0.0.1]\";\n213771-\t} catch {\n213772-\t\treturn false;\n213773-\t}\n213774-}\n213775-function hasExplicitProviderApiKeyConfig(providerConfig) {\n213776-\treturn normalizeOptionalSecretInput(providerConfig.apiKey) !== void 0 || coerceSecretRef(providerConfig.apiKey) !== null;\n213777-}\n213778-function isCustomLocalProviderConfig(providerConfig) {\n213779-\treturn typeof providerConfig.baseUrl === \"string\" && providerConfig.baseUrl.trim().length > 0 && typeof providerConfig.api === \"string\" && providerConfig.api.trim().length > 0 && Array.isArray(providerConfig.models) && providerConfig.models.length > 0;\n213780-}\n213781-function isManagedSecretRefApiKeyMarker(apiKey) {\n213782-\treturn apiKey?.trim() === NON_ENV_SECRETREF_MARKER;\n213783-}\n213784-function resolveProviderSyntheticRuntimeAuth(params) {\n213785-\tconst resolveFromConfig = (config) => {\n213786-\t\tconst providerConfig = resolveProviderConfig(config, params.provider);\n213787-\t\treturn resolveProviderSyntheticAuthWithPlugin({"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":88,"aggregated":"213767:function isLocalBaseUrl(baseUrl) {\n213768-\ttry {\n213769-\t\tconst host = new URL(baseUrl).hostname.toLowerCase();\n213770-\t\treturn host === \"localhost\" || host === \"127.0.0.1\" || host === \"0.0.0.0\" || host === \"[::1]\" || host === \"[::ffff:7f00:1]\" || host === \"[::ffff:127.0.0.1]\";\n213771-\t} catch {\n213772-\t\treturn false;\n213773-\t}\n213774-}\n213775-function hasExplicitProviderApiKeyConfig(providerConfig) {\n213776-\treturn normalizeOptionalSecretInput(providerConfig.apiKey) !== void 0 || coerceSecretRef(providerConfig.apiKey) !== null;\n213777-}\n213778-function isCustomLocalProviderConfig(providerConfig) {\n213779-\treturn typeof providerConfig.baseUrl === \"string\" && providerConfig.baseUrl.trim().length > 0 && typeof providerConfig.api === \"string\" && providerConfig.api.trim().length > 0 && Array.isArray(providerConfig.models) && providerConfig.models.length > 0;\n213780-}\n213781-function isManagedSecretRefApiKeyMarker(apiKey) {\n213782-\treturn apiKey?.trim() === NON_ENV_SECRETREF_MARKER;\n213783-}\n213784-function resolveProviderSyntheticRuntimeAuth(params) {\n213785-\tconst resolveFromConfig = (config) => {\n213786-\t\tconst providerConfig = resolveProviderConfig(config, params.provider);\n213787-\t\treturn resolveProviderSyntheticAuthWithPlugin({","cwd":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775547794885}}
{"type":"message","id":"d22d7372","parentId":"155cac9b","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:43:21.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！现在我完全明白问题了：\n\n**问题分析：**\n1. `isLocalBaseUrl()` 只接受：`localhost`、`127.0.0.1`、`0.0.0.0`、`[::1]` —— 不包含公网 IP\n2. 你的 baseUrl 是 `http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1`，这是公网 IP，所以无法触发自动合成认证\n3. 同时你删除了 provider 配置中的 `apiKey` 字段，所以 `customKey` 检查也找不到\n4. `auth-profiles.json` 里虽然有 profile，但 OpenClaw 没有正确读取到？不对，让我们回到前面...\n\n实际上，代码逻辑是：`resolveSyntheticLocalProviderAuth` 只有在 `hasExplicitProviderApiKeyConfig` 返回 `false` 时才会继续。那我们把 `apiKey` 加回去，让它存在但为空，看看会发生什么：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kkixgh52aw7ksme1oker6esh","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json","oldText":"      \"local-gpu\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\",\n        \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n        \"models\": [","newText":"      \"local-gpu\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"\",\n        \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n        \"models\": ["}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":6477,"output":425,"cacheRead":22840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775547794887,"responseId":"021775547795002289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108ae259786"}}
