{"type":"message","id":"ac6da843","parentId":"1ccd490e","timestamp":"2026-04-07T08:01:54.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！这里配置错误：\n\n- vLLM 提供的是 **OpenAI 兼容格式** 的 API\n- 但当前配置中 `api` 设置为了 `anthropic-messages`，这是 Anthropic 的格式，完全不兼容\n\n所以 OpenClaw 用错误的格式请求你的 vLLM 服务，vLLM 无法识别，所以不会返回正确响应，导致超时。\n\n让我修正这个问题：\n\n| 位置 | 当前值 | 正确值 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| provider `api` | `anthropic-messages` | `openai` |\n| model `api` | `anthropic-messages` | `openai` |\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_86fab3b1dcpk7w7glry5ac1k","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json","oldText":"      \"local-gpu\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"\",\n        \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b\",\n            \"name\": \"Qwen3.5 35B A3B (Local GPU)\",\n            \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\",","newText":"      \"local-gpu\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"http://112.226.133.33:12345/v1\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"\",\n        \"api\": \"openai\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b\",\n            \"name\": \"Qwen3.5 35B A3B (Local GPU)\",\n            \"api\": \"openai\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\","}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":534,"output":501,"cacheRead":36152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775548902113,"responseId":"021775548902285e8eb33bba790666117f5ace3387e184269a447"}}
